[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    148[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mLocation:[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m Step 6 pseudocode [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140minvalidate_on_event[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m source [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140m"document_upgrade"[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m: "A previously self-reported change now has a supporting document (a court order arrived, a marriage certificate was scanned). The event's source_strength is upgraded; the resolution may move from REVIEW_PENDING to AUTO_RESOLVE if it was held for review." Honest Take's "Document-strength promotion edge cases" paragraph.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    149[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mProblem:[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m The recipe correctly identifies the document-strength-promotion path but does not specify the audit posture for this consequential event type. A document that arrives weeks after a self-reported change retroactively promotes the resolution from MEDIUM-WEAK to STRONG source, may shift the effective date from the self-report date to the document-extracted legal-change date, and may automatically resolve a previously-pending review-queue item. The audit trail should capture the document hash, the upload provenance, the extraction-engine output, the reviewer-verification (where applicable), and the retroactive resolution adjustment with explicit "document-strength-promotion" attribution distinct from "automated" or "reviewer-confirmed."[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    150[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mFix:[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m Add to the persistence paragraph or the audit posture: [38;2;180;142;173m*[38;2;180;142;173m"Document-strength-promotion events carry their own audit attribution ([38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mresolved_by: \"document-strength-promotion\"[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;180;142;173m) with the document hash, the upload provenance, the extraction-engine version and confidence, the reviewer-verification reference where applicable, and the prior-resolution-state-id for forensic reconstruction. The retroactive effective-date adjustment (from self-report date to document-extracted legal-change date) is logged as a separate audit entry with full evidence."[38;2;180;142;173m*[K
