[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    178[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mProblem:[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m Same chapter pattern as 5.1 / 5.2 / 5.3 / 5.4 / 5.5 / 5.6 Finding A2. The recipe explicitly inherits the rigor ("applies here too") and the production-gaps section names the suggested values, but the architecture pattern does not specify the cohort-axis enumeration, the disparity-calculation method, the per-metric emission cadence, or the remediation pathway. Six concrete gaps:[K
